subproject.description: To address sedimentation in the Lake’s inflowing rivers by devising and implementing cross-sectoral measures to limit soil erosion and seek deforestation through promotion of: Natural resource management practices that increase productivity and resource conservation; Entrepreneurial skills for productive alternative income generating activities to reduce pressures on land resources; Local governance structures for sustainable natural resource management in local communities.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
subproject.title: Sediment control-Lk Tanganyik
